messages.messageBody:
-----Original Message-----
From: Karin
Hi Shannon!

I went and looked at your photo album pictures and they turned out great! I
love all your added little captions, too. Then I saw the picture you took of
me and Bryan - I didn't even know you took that! I was too busy feeding my
face, but I guess Bryan noticed and even smiled for the pic. :-)

Thanks for sharing those pictures! Can't believe that was only a week ago.
It seems like it was at least a month ago, for some reason.

Karin


Glad you liked the pictures, Karin. I was just trying to get impromptu
pictures at the park. I was glad that Bryan smiled for me, tho. I kwym
about the conference seeming so long ago. I so wish Dave and Connor could
ve gone. I end up saying that A LOT to Dave and he is getting really tired
of hearing it. Lol Maybe itll make him try a little harder next year to
go with me. ;o)

Shan
